
** Diagnostics Pack

  - Automatic capturing of AWR data
  - Performance analysis based on AWR (ADDM)
  - OS monitoring
  - Adaptive thresholds. Compare against baselines.
  - Advanced alert management		
  - Retrieve performance statistics directly from the SGA

** Tuning Pack

  - SQL Tuning Advisor
  - SQL Access Advisor (indices, MVs)
  - Reorganize objects
  - SQL Tuning sets (capture SQL workloads)

** Change Management Pack

  - Baselines
  - Comparsions
  - Synchonization

** Configuration Management Pack

  - Conf. management (search, comparsion, change tracking, reporting)
  - Patching
  - Policy and security management
  - Policy groups (database, listener, rac)

** Provisioning Pack for Database

  - Patching
    - Oracle products
    - Linux
    - Windows
    - Solaris
  - Provisioning and Cloning
    - OS
    - Images of db, rac and as
    - extend rac and as
    - clone DBs and $OHs
    - convert single-instance DBs to RAC

